s=\"text-gray-500 text-base leading-relaxed mt-8 max-w-md\" style=\"opacity:0\">The rarest drops never make it to the public. Syndicate members get first look, first claim, and zero FOMO. Submit your credentials to gain clearance.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-5 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#111] border border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-blue-900 group-hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bell text-blue-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0\"></path><path d=\"M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">Early Drop Access</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-1\">New vault entries hit your inbox 24hrs before public release.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-5 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#111] border border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-blue-900 group-hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield text-blue-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">Verified Collector Badge</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-1\">Exclusive Syndicate member status across all communications.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-5 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-[#111] border border-gray-800 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-blue-900 group-hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap text-blue-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider\">Flash Sale Alerts</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-1\">Instant notification when prices drop or rare units surface.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-900\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"flex -space-x-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-900 border-2 border-[#050505] flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-black text-white\">A</div><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-900 border-2 border-[#050505] flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-black text-white\">B</div><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-900 border-2 border-[#050505] flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-black text-white\">C</div><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-900 border-2 border-[#050505] flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-black text-white\">D</div></div><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest\">Collectors already inside the Vault</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px) scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-800 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 md:p-14 relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 bg-blue-600/5 blur-[60px] rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none\"></div><div style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"mb-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock text-blue-600 mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-white italic tracking-tighter\">Request Clearance</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mt-2\">Syndicate application form</p></div><form class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-black uppercase tracking-widest\">Operative Name <span class=\"text-gray-700 normal-case\">(optional)</span></label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your name...\" class=\"w-full bg-[#050505] border border-gray-800 text-white p-4 font-bold text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-600 transition-colors placeholder:text-gray-700\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-black uppercase tracking-widest\">Secure Comms Channel <span class=\"text-red-600\">*</span></label><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"your@email.com\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full bg-[#050505] border border-gray-800 text-white p-4 font-bold text-sm focus:outline-n